fields.title: Senior Python Developer
fields.description: We're looking for a senior Python developer to join our growing team. You'll work on building scalable web applications using Django, PostgreSQL, and AWS. Experience with Docker and Kubernetes preferred.

fields.title: Frontend React Developer
fields.description: Join our frontend team to build beautiful, responsive user interfaces. We use React, TypeScript, and modern CSS frameworks. Experience with state management libraries like Redux is a plus.

fields.title: Full-Stack Developer
fields.description: We need a versatile developer who can work across the entire stack. Our tech stack includes Django, React, PostgreSQL, and Redis. You'll be involved in both backend API development and frontend user interfaces.

fields.title: DevOps Engineer
fields.description: Help us scale our infrastructure and improve our deployment processes. Experience with AWS, Docker, Kubernetes, and CI/CD pipelines required. Python scripting skills preferred.

fields.title: Data Scientist
fields.description: Join our data team to build machine learning models and analyze large datasets. We use Python, pandas, scikit-learn, and TensorFlow. Experience with SQL and data visualization tools preferred.

fields.title: Backend API Developer
fields.description: Build robust REST APIs using Django and Django REST Framework. You'll work with PostgreSQL, Redis, and various third-party integrations. Experience with API design and documentation is essential.

fields.title: Mobile App Developer
fields.description: Develop cross-platform mobile applications using React Native. You'll work closely with our design team to create intuitive user experiences. Experience with native iOS/Android development is a bonus.

fields.title: UI/UX Designer
fields.description: Create beautiful and functional user interfaces for our web and mobile applications. You'll work with Figma, Adobe Creative Suite, and collaborate closely with developers. Experience with design systems preferred.

fields.title: Database Administrator
fields.description: Manage and optimize our PostgreSQL databases. You'll be responsible for performance tuning, backup strategies, and ensuring data integrity. Experience with database monitoring tools required.

fields.title: Security Engineer
fields.description: Protect our systems and data from security threats. You'll conduct security audits, implement security policies, and respond to incidents. Experience with penetration testing and security tools preferred.

fields.title: Product Manager
fields.description: Lead product development from conception to launch. You'll work with engineering, design, and business teams to define product requirements and prioritize features. Technical background preferred.

fields.title: QA Engineer
fields.description: Ensure our software meets quality standards through comprehensive testing. You'll write test cases, perform manual testing, and work with automated testing frameworks. Experience with Selenium preferred.

fields.title: Technical Writer
fields.description: Create clear and comprehensive documentation for our APIs, user guides, and technical specifications. You'll work closely with developers to understand complex systems and translate them into user-friendly content.

fields.title: Cloud Architect
fields.description: Design and implement cloud infrastructure solutions using AWS, Azure, or Google Cloud. You'll work on scalability, security, and cost optimization. Experience with Infrastructure as Code tools preferred.

fields.title: Machine Learning Engineer
fields.description: Build and deploy machine learning models in production environments. You'll work with Python, TensorFlow, PyTorch, and cloud ML services. Experience with MLOps and model monitoring preferred.

fields.title: Software Engineer - Midtown Atlanta
fields.description: Join our Midtown engineering team building web platforms with Django, React, and PostgreSQL. Collaborate across product and design.

fields.title: Backend Developer - Buckhead
fields.description: Build and scale backend services and APIs in Django. Experience with Celery, Redis, and cloud deployments a plus.
